### Health check
GET http://localhost:8000/health

###
### Upload a single PDF (replace path with a real file)
### Use the REST Client extension in VSCode (humao.rest-client)

POST http://localhost:8000/api/parse
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="extract_name"

true
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="extract_position"

true
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="extract_phone"

true
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="extract_email"

true
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="languages"

eng,tha
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="empty_value"

null
--boundary--

###
### Get batch status (replace BATCH_ID)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/batch/BATCH_ID

###
### Download Excel (replace BATCH_ID)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/export/BATCH_ID
